      "text": "No one put it there.\n\nNo wonder I haven't been able to figure 3-74 out; every theory changes the events. I was right when I was on superdope; then I favored the theory that Diana, the queen of the fairies, helped me. Now I prefer (and find more workable) the theory that it was the Holy Spirit revealsing to me the Cosmic Christ (Valis).\n\nThere's one thing I know it is: the Mysterium Coniunctionis. In Boehme's terminology (or Eckhart; who cares) you have become the Father, not the Son; therefore y",
      "matched_alias": "Eckhart",
      "term_id": "TERM_eckhart",
      "term_name": "Eckhart",
      "term_slug": "eckhart"
    },
    {
      "text": "This means that behind bitheism lies monotheism. It is as if the revelation of the dialectic is in itself a secret —first revealed to Zoroaster— but there is a further secret concealed within that secret: that behind the dialectic lies unity, and both sides in the dialectic are good, hence both are \"good\" insofar as \"good\" is involved at all: Satan is God in a Satan-suit. In the cosmic game, the Godhead is playing against itself! Its wisdom against its creative power!\n\nAnd the reason for all thi",
      "matched_alias": "Form World",
      "term_id": "TERM_form-world",
      "term_name": "Form World",
      "term_slug": "form-world"
    }
